name: “001.How To Play” 10/28/21 @goneyharlic
description:
(30/30)
3000x3000,300dpi.jpg

I love multiple types/styles of digital collage. With trying to make /burnedbyairfryer have a more surreal themed foundation & /fiasco9.0 being more digitally manipulated abstractions..I wanted to create a collage series where I attempt to be more experimental with the placement of assets with very little edits to them...kind of wanting to replicate a more minimal & analog look with a fun problem solving / loose puzzle piecing creative experience. Maybe breaking rules here and there, but definitely wanting to just bring highlight to the the combination of assets themselves, rather than a conceptualized piece. Also I really really need to practice simplicity...Even in this practice it's hard to contain, I'm just always seeing for what can be added. @goneyharlic is just about loosely being what it is..An experimental digital collage through my eyes and vibes at that moment. Also been working more on 1/1s with the other collections, but I decided for this series to be more widely available as a thank you for any collectors accepting this personal aesthetic.
Experimental digital collage created with photoshop.
